1
00:00:06,930 --> 00:00:09,430
The Grand Tutor's mansion must be a blessed place.

2
00:00:09,430 --> 00:00:11,230
It makes one reluctant to leave.

3
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:13,630
Then I won't force you.

4
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:22,260
In that case,

5
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:23,730
I might as well stay here too.

6
00:00:23,730 --> 00:00:24,400
This...

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,430
How can this be?

8
00:00:25,430 --> 00:00:26,900
You are an important minister of the court, General.

9
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:27,960
Condescending to stay in my humble mansion

10
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:28,800
is truly inappropriate.

11
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:29,730
What?

12
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,800
Don't you have guest rooms?

13
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:34,460
If you don't have guest rooms,

14
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:36,530
the three of you can get out and sleep on the streets.

15
00:00:36,530 --> 00:00:38,060
Give your courtyard to me.

16
00:00:38,060 --> 00:00:39,860
No, we do.

17
00:00:39,860 --> 00:00:41,760
We have plenty of excellent guest rooms.

18
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:44,020
You may stay as long as you like, General.

19
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:53,860
Let me go.

20
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,400
What exactly are you up to?

21
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:57,600
Make it clear,

22
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,830
or you won't leave today.

23
00:01:03,630 --> 00:01:04,959
The indentures of all the women in my family

24
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,260
are in the hands of the Wei family.

25
00:01:06,260 --> 00:01:07,400
Cut the nonsense.

26
00:01:07,830 --> 00:01:09,430
If it's just for the indentures,

27
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,800
I'll go to Grand Tutor Wei right now

28
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:13,130
and ask for all your family's indentures.

29
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,830
Even if you take them by force today,

30
00:01:14,830 --> 00:01:17,160
wouldn't Grand Tutor Wei impeach you tomorrow?

31
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:19,330
Your reputation as General Weibei is already unruly.

32
00:01:19,330 --> 00:01:20,360
If you add this to it,

33
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:21,800
do you still want your future?

34
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,000
I don't want a future.

35
00:01:23,630 --> 00:01:24,730
I just want you.

36
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:29,360
Lu Jingxing.

37
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,760
If you are stripped of your military power because of this

38
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,600
and lose your status and influence,

39
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:36,560
I would make the same choice I made three years ago anytime.

40
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,030
A man whose head is full of romance

41
00:01:38,030 --> 00:01:39,360
and who lacks ambition,

42
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:41,259
I, Shen Lvyi, look down upon.

43
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,000
Do you treat me as a human

44
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,330
or a dog you keep?

45
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:53,660
What right do you have to say these things to me now?

46
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,920
I'm no longer your stable boy, Shen Lvyi.

47
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:57,800
And you are no longer my master.

48
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,460
Sister.

49
00:02:08,460 --> 00:02:09,160
Lvyi,

50
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,460
it's been hard on you.

51
00:02:10,729 --> 00:02:12,530
I regret it so much.

52
00:02:12,530 --> 00:02:14,760
If I had known you would be wronged like this today,

53
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:17,460
I should have let you and that boy be together back then.

54
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:20,230
Mother, let's not talk about the past.

55
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,800
Over the past three days,

56
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,130
have you been following my previous plan?

57
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:26,030
Is everything going smoothly?

58
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,530
I sneaked into Lady Wei's room.

59
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,760
Under the guise of cleaning,

60
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,960
I searched her whole room,

61
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:39,860
but there was no trace of the posthumous edict.

62
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:49,230
We've searched Grand Tutor Wei's study for the past three days.

63
00:02:49,230 --> 00:02:50,860
We didn't miss a single corner,

64
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:52,860
but we didn't find the edict either.

65
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,860
Your father received the late Emperor's edict back then

66
00:02:57,860 --> 00:02:59,560
and always kept it safe.

67
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:02,200
But it vanished into thin air on the day our house was raided.

68
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,260
If the edict was not in the hands of

69
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:05,300
Grand Tutor Wei, who presided over the raid at the time,

70
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:06,700
where else could it be?

71
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:08,260
Could it have been

72
00:03:08,260 --> 00:03:09,930
burned by Grand Tutor Wei?

73
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:10,900
No.

74
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,760
The one who wants to destroy the late Emperor's edict the most is His Majesty.

75
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,360
If Grand Tutor Wei wanted to burn the edict,

76
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,200
he would definitely present it to His Majesty to destroy first.

77
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:19,260
The storehouse in the backyard is locked.

78
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:21,000
We never had a chance to get in.

79
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,860
Could it be in the storehouse?

80
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:23,600
But

81
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:26,660
the storehouse is only opened for inventory during festivals.

82
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:28,660
Normally, no one is allowed near it.

83
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:32,190
There is another day when the storehouse will be opened.

84
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:33,900
When Wei Yingying gets engaged.

85
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,600
When the betrothal gifts arrive,

86
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,030
the storehouse must be opened

87
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,400
to store them.

88
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:41,700
But I heard General Weibei is arrogant and unruly.

89
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:44,760
Grand Tutor Wei invited him several times to discuss the marriage,

90
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,020
but he refused to come.

91
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:49,190
He seems very dissatisfied with this marriage.

92
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:53,500
It's hard to say when he will send the betrothal gifts.

93
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:56,460
Then we can only hope General Weibei takes pity

94
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:58,660
and sends the gifts as soon as possible.

95
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:01,130
I'm going out.

96
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,760
I might not come back tonight.

97
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,860
Rest early

98
00:04:03,930 --> 00:04:04,900
and be careful.

99
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,800
Lu Jingxing is reckless and arrogant.

100
00:04:15,830 --> 00:04:17,930
He responds to persuasion, not coercion.

101
00:04:17,930 --> 00:04:20,560
If I directly tell him to send the gifts early,

102
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,620
I'm afraid I'll poke the bear.

103
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:26,300
I must find a way to coax him properly.

104
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,730
Had I known this,

105
00:04:34,060 --> 00:04:37,520
I shouldn't have said those harsh words to him this afternoon.

106
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:40,830
The General is mighty and majestic.

107
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:42,659
I fell in love with you at first sight.

108
00:04:42,659 --> 00:04:44,430
To be engaged to you

109
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,930
and be your wife for a lifetime,

110
00:04:45,930 --> 00:04:48,430
I am truly overjoyed.

111
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:50,800
This Second Miss Wei is so annoying with her blabbering.

112
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,200
Should I knock her out with a chop and throw her out,

113
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,930
or just draw my sword and scare her into fainting?

114
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:05,300
You have a great capacity for liquor, General.

115
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,630
You are so imposing!

116
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:18,330
See that?

117
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:19,900
I'm highly sought after.

118
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:22,230
Aren't you going to come in and coax me?

119
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:24,800
General.

120
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:26,230
What's wrong?

121
00:05:28,460 --> 00:05:30,790
It seems they are mutually affectionate.

122
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,400
Sending the gifts and getting married is only a matter of time.

123
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,700
It looks like I don't need to worry about it.

124
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:36,700
Stop right there.

125
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,000
Get in here

126
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,230
and serve me wine.

127
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,690
What are you doing here?

128
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,400
Running into a man's room in the middle of the night,

129
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,730
have you no shame?

130
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:57,190
Aren't you here too?

131
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:59,300
Brother Jingxing.

132
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:00,900
How can she compare to me?

133
00:06:01,030 --> 00:06:02,960
The General and I are engaged.

134
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:03,830
You freaking...

135
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:06,400
The General and the Second Miss are a match made in heaven.

136
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,630
I wish you two a speedy marriage,

137
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:09,860
eternal love,

138
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:11,360
and growing old together.

139
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,690
You certainly know how to talk.

140
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,620
General, quickly drink this cup of wine.

141
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:21,260
Crap.

142
00:06:21,330 --> 00:06:22,660
Did I overact just now

143
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:23,990
and really make her mad?

144
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:26,690
It's all this troublemaker's fault.

145
00:06:31,630 --> 00:06:32,530
Drink my ass!

146
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,000
I told you to leave as soon as you came in.

147
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,030
But you keep throwing yourself at me.

148
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:36,230
Aren't you annoying?

149
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:39,560
General, you were drinking fine just now.

150
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,030
Why did you turn on me

151
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,130
as soon as this bitch came in?

152
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:46,730
It's all my fault.

153
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,130
Please calm down, Second Miss.

154
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:50,300
It's because you are shameless,

155
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,600
seducing my fiancé.

156
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:53,560
General, don't be bewitched by this bitch.

157
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,560
She is a total slut.

158
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:57,860
When she was the Eldest Miss of the Minister's Manor,

159
00:06:57,860 --> 00:06:59,790
she had an affair with a stable boy.

160
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:01,430
They were so deeply in love.

161
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:02,730
So despicable.

162
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:04,520
Mind your words, Second Miss.

163
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:07,330
You did such scandalous things,

164
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:09,320
but you're afraid I'll spread it?

165
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:11,060
I just want the General to know

166
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:14,320
that you are a bitch who fell in love with her own stable boy.

167
00:07:16,330 --> 00:07:17,230
General.

168
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:22,930
Even Wei Er knew that the Eldest Miss fell in love with me back then.

169
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:26,590
General, why are you still looking at that bitch?

170
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,760
If you scold her again,

171
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,930
I'll slit your mouth to your ears.

172
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,360
Lu Jingxing!

173
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:49,030
I'm here.
